                            <p class="text-left leading-relaxed text-gray-800 text-sm mb-5 pl-0 md:pl-5"><strong>The 2020 pandemic forced Green FM to shift from airwaves to digital platforms</strong>, launching DLSU-D Green FM Podcasts on Facebook, Spotify, and Apple Podcasts. As Green FM enters a new academic year, it aims to revive traditional programming while embracing digital trends and enhancing its content with robust blocktimer collaborations from De La Salle University–Dasmariñas organizations and communities.</p>
